Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.37,0:02:29.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:33.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't really know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:36.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He came asking about the "Rebirths".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:38.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:41.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did he hear about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:49.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I come so far and find nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:52.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Islanders are sure hard to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:57.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll take my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.29,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is that light over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:18.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They seem too bright to be Umibotaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:20.97,notes,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(150,150)\be1}Umibotaru: Sea Fireflies (Vargula Hilgendorfii)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's too small to be fishing lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:24.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:27.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can see it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:34.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know much about those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:35.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:38.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's how I make a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:40.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:43.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandpa's back. Let's have dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:45.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's that man from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:50.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:53.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's too many snakes to camp out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:59.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:00.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:02.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well now, that's rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:05.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is he, Mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:07.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Isana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:12.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah sorry, Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:37.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think it'll show up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The moon's rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:43.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:45.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:50.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you come here to find out about the "Rebirths"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:54.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:05:02.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That light always appears by that boulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:08.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a deep chasm there that we call the "Ryuuguu".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:15.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone who dies there is reborn exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:23.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did Isana look like a normal child?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:26.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:27.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:32.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,the Rebirth of my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:36.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:42.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:47.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mio, no one has ever survived this sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:51.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to submerge her while she's\Nstill alive or she can't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:52.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:54.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:57.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:06:05.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid of vanishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:15.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to sleep knowing I'll be back here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:18.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:20.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:38.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mio, it's the full moon tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:44.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to see Mom again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:48.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to see her and so do our relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:51.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's waiting for Mana to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:58.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's been difficult for you to have\Nlost both your husband and mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:07:02.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's why it'll be even better\Nfor you if you bear a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:04.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:12.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:17.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If seeing her will make everyone happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:19.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll give birth to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:24.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that child isn't Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Promise me that we won't call her Mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,One is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:42.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:45.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If you become pregnant,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:50.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,it'll become the child that was\Nsubmerged within the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:07.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's how Isana was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:12.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Couldn't it have been your dead husband's child?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:17.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was two years before Isana was\Nborn that my husband died.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:23.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to know what that child is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:29.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't say just yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:32.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but she seems like a normal human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:35.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No doubt, she's the child that\Nyou pained yourself to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:41.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you think of her as\Nher grandmother's look-alike?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mio,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:08:58.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:03.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here's what I do when I can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:06.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I pretend I'm a big fish
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:14.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and that I'm diving down into a deep, blue sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:19.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And before I know it, I'm asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:23.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:27.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:30.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good night, Isana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:34.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:40.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yup, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:45.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Grandma's "Rebirth".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:47.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:49.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, over there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:55.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was reborn after he almost died from a snake bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:58.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That lady over there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:03.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was attacked by a shark right after she got married
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:07.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and her husband waited over ten years to wed her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:13.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's living happily after being reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:17.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you happy too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:21.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It bothers me a little when people call me Mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:24.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:26.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom doesn't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:29.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm happy that I was born to Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:34.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I like this island and the sea too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:54.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:58.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be safe approaching the light at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:01.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll wait for the spawning on the full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:03.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So are you staying here until then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:04.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:09.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow. Look, it's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:20.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,An island where lost loved ones can be brought back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:25.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forever, if desired – never to part.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:29.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then this must be utopia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:32.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:40.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought she resembled my mother\Nwhen she was a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:46.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what my mother looked\Nlike when she was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:52.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But as she grows older, her face changes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:58.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,her character, even her little habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:01.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything becomes more and more\Nlike the mother that I used to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:07.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I swear I'd parted with my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:12.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet here she is looking just like\Nher, calling me her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:18.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I gave birth to this child and raised her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:22.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I can't think of her as my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's from deep inside the "Ryuuguu".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:37.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm certain it's a Mushi creating those grains.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:43.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure, but here's my theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:48.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I found inside the grain was the\N"embryos" of various creatures –
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,the very fundamental form of every animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:58.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,For those who consume it to bear children\Nidentical to those that were submerged...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:06.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,must mean that the Mushi has the ability to restore\Nan organism to its original embryological form.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:11.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:16.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your child is physically identical to your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:20.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She'll become even more like your mother in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:26.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, she was raised by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:31.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So she'll never become your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:38.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're her mother, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:45.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:50.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got to pull myself together for her sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:02.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:08.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be leaving tomorrow if it's safe to set sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:16.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't know what to do if I stay here any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:21.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have the right to take away your happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:31.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:38.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to give birth to Mom if she's about to die too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:42.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine my mom being gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:51.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should think it over for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:53.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might be a typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:57.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:05.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's raining pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:09.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have trouble sleeping sometimes too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:13.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course. But I know a good trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:15.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you can't sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:20.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,try pretending that you're a big\Nfish diving deep into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:26.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You go past the corals, beyond the suckerfish...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:31.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go deep, deep into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That'll make you really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:36.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:38.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:42.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:46.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. Just stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:57.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to pull myself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's going to get washed away out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:23.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:26.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:28.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't find my boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:29.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. She couldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:32.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:38.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:40.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Isana!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:43.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't go near that light. You'll be eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:47.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't rush off like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:49.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going to go carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:55.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:58.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're surrounding the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:00.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:01.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isana!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:04.31,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:06.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! Isana!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:34.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:37.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isana, how about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:38.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:42.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get up, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:18:59.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:04.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm really hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:15.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it going to consume and restore me to an embryo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:22.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To the point before everything begins?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:33.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah, that's not a nice thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:46.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm being pulled away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:59.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get on, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:04.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The storm's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:11.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did it suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:21.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:25.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:39.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've only learned a little bit about the Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:43.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It attracts prey with its light, consumes them,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:49.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then restores them back to their basic form.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:54.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could call it a Mushi that "consumes\Nthe days of its prey's life".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:59.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, you know about it quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:05.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you can sort out all your problems over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:08.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:12.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Isama. You weren't thinking when\Nyou jumped in there, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:15.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I almost got a heart attack, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:17.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:24.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though you could have met your\Nmom again if you gave birth to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:26.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:32.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but then it would've eaten all the\Ntime that Mom lived, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:34.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's too sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:38.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she's going to have everything\Nin her life taken away from her,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:43.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd rather she died while she's still Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:49.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just like Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:55.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sure are my kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:11.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I assume there'll be more "Rebirths" at the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:16.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,To comfort the dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.81,0:22:21.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,To fill in the gaps for their survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:27.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,To die without wishing for such
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.74,0:22:31.12,dialogue,,0,0,0,,may be a priceless joy.
